  "prompt": "What do I get for answering questions in Quora?",
  "response": "On Quora, users can:\n\n1. Gain social reputation through:\n- Upvotes on your answers\n- Views on your content\n- Followers who appreciate your knowledge\n- A reputation score that increases with quality contributions\n\n2. Non-monetary rewards like:\n- Recognition as a knowledgeable contributor\n- Establishing expertise in specific topics\n- Personal satisfaction from helping others\n- Potential networking opportunities\n\n3. Optional Quora Partner Program (limited availability):\n- Some users can earn money for asking questions that generate high engagement\n- Not available to all users and has specific qualification criteria\n\n4. No direct monetary compensation for most answers:\n- Most contributions are voluntary\n- Users participate to share knowledge, not for financial gain\n\nQuora is primarily a knowledge-sharing platform where users contribute content to help others and build their online reputation.",
